harbinger capital partners about us our history about us harbinger capital partners is a private investment firm specializing in eventdistressed strategies founded in  with philip falcone as the chief investment officer harbinger capital partners seeks to invest in alphagenerating ideas that are uncorrelated to investment cycles harbinger seeks investments that typically fall into the following four categories event – investments in companies where the harbinger team identifies a significant opportunity to actively engage with a company to unlock value distressedbankruptcy – investments in companies that are already in default in bankruptcy or in some other stage of financial failure or distress value – passive investments in securities where harbinger believes a positive catalyst for value realization is already present and corporate shorts – passive investments where harbinger views the security to be overvalued or believes weakening fundamental trends or identifiable negative catalysts are apparent philip falcone leads harbingers investment team relying on his extensive experience in distressed debt leveraged finance and special situations across an array of market cycles  harbinger capital partners all rights reserved      privacy policy harbinger capital partners about us our history our history in  philip falcone capitalized on the significant opportunities within the distressed marketplace and became the chief investment officer of harbinger capital partners upon its inception through conviction in his ability to identify value in creditdistressed mr falcone led an investment team focused on opportunities in credit over the next few years as the distressed credit market subsided and the broader investment universe became more sophisticated harbinger adjusted its strategy accordingly and as most investment firms focused upon distressed opportunities do evolved into special situation and event strategies as well with extensive experience in several different strategies harbinger was able to respond to market fluctuations over time with rigor efficiency and builtin flexibility as harbinger reached a critical mass it was able to engage proactively with companies in order to enhance value although harbingers expansion since its inception has been substantial the underlying work ethic and conviction to succeed the principles on which the company was started continue to define harbinger capital partners today  harbinger capital partners all rights reserved      privacy policy harbinger capital partners contact us harbinger capital partners  park avenue th floor new york ny  phone   or   email clientserviceharbingercapitalcom media inquiries paul holmes rlm finsbury phone   email paulholmesrlmfinsburycom  harbinger capital partners all rights reserved      privacy policy harbinger capital partners harbinger capital partners harbinger capital partners  midtown east   park ave foursquarelog insign upnearbyget inspiredtop pickstrendingfoodcoffeenightlifefunshoppingplanning a trip to new yorkfoursquare can help you find the best places to go tofind great things to doharbinger capital partnersofficemidtown east new yorksavesharetipsharbinger capital partnersno tips and reviewslog in to leave a tip herepostno tips yetwrite a short note about what you liked what to order or other helpful advice for visitors photorelated searchesharbinger capital partners new york  harbinger capital partners new york photos  harbinger capital partners new york location  harbinger capital partners new york address  harbinger capital partners new york  harbinger capital partners new york  harbinger capital partners midtown east new yorkaboutblogbusinessescitiesdevelopershelpjobscookies updatedprivacy updatedtermsenglishenglish français deutsch bahasa indonesia italiano  한국어 português русский español ภาษาไทย türkçe citiesatlantaaustinbostonchicagodallasdenverhoustonlas vegaslos angelesnew yorkphiladelphiaportlandsan diegosan franciscoseattlewashingt